To run the enhanced TaskMaster, use the following commands:

Add a task: python taskmaster.py add Remind me to buy groceries tomorrow at 5 PM
List tasks: python taskmaster.py list
Complete a task: python taskmaster.py complete 0
Edit a task: python taskmaster.py edit 0 Buy vegetables instead
Delete a task: python taskmaster.py delete 0
Search tasks: python taskmaster.py search buy
Save tasks: python taskmaster.py save
Load tasks: python taskmaster.py load
Show help: python taskmaster.py help
